Query on what does

No value set at Extension.valueCoding (url = 'https://healthterminologies.gov.au/fhir/ValueSet/australian-indigenous-status-1')

mean in IG build log? Is this a GET with Accept header set failing ?
following up on this one - is the IG builder looking for a resource? are redirects possible?

AU base build will do it ... IG comes out okay (link reproduced in the IG); but wondering if there is more I should be asking out of the https://healthterminologies.gov.au/fhir/ValueSet/australian-indigenous-status-1 resolution...
what more could you want? you provide an external URI, you get a reference to it?
